caller_intent: Gary needed assistance resolving an issue where a signed document was not being properly transferred back to Alliance Insurance Services after signing.
resolution_steps: Michael confirmed the document signing process with Gary.
Michael instructed Gary to click the 'complete' button at the top of the document after signing to ensure it was sent back.
Michael offered to mail the document as an alternative if the digital process failed.
systems_referenced: Email client (mention of sent items and email confirmation)
summary: Gary contacted Michael Adamson to resolve an issue where a signed document was not being transferred back after signing. Michael guided Gary to use the 'complete' button in the document interface and offered mailing as a backup. The call concluded with Gary agreeing to follow the steps and contact back if needed.
